Package com.vangav.backend.play_framework.request

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Request
    Request contains the request, its response, dispatcher buffer, exception, and everything about a request-response pair.
    RequestHeader
    RequestHeader represents a request's header
    RequestJsonBody
    RequestJsonBody is the parent class for a controller's json body with POST and GET children which act as sub-parents for defining the json structure of the request
    RequestJsonBodyGet
    RequestJsonBodyGet is the parent class for GET requests children classes define the request's structure
    RequestJsonBodyPost
    RequestJsonBodyPost is the parent class for POST requests children classes define the request's structure
    RequestProperties
    RequestProperties is the properties file with boolean switches that controls the processing sequence of a request
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RequestState
    enum RequestState (OK, BAD_REQUEST, etc ...)
    RequestType
    enum RequestType (POST, GET, etc ...)
